# NeuraPilot 🧠

> **Production-grade Agentic RAG Tutor** — compound AI pipeline with LangGraph,
> semantic caching, real-time observability, and multi-modal understanding.

[![Python 3.11](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.11-blue.svg)](https://python.org)
[![LangGraph](https://img.shields.io/badge/LangGraph-0.2-green.svg)](https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/)
[![Streamlit](https://img.shields.io/badge/Streamlit-1.35-red.svg)](https://streamlit.io)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-ready-blue.svg)](./Dockerfile)

---

## 📐 System Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        NeuraPilot — Data Flow                           │
│                                                                         │
│  ┌──────────┐   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │  USER    │──▶│               Streamlit UI                       │    │
│  │ (browser)│   │  chat · quiz · flashcards · visualize · study    │    │
│  └──────────┘   └───────────────────┬─────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                      │ user query                        │
│                  ┌───────────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐   │
│                  │            Semantic Cache (SQLite)                │   │
│                  │   embed → cosine sim ≥ 0.92 → HIT (~120 ms)      │   │
│                  └──────────────┬───────────────┬───────────────────┘   │
│                           MISS  │               │ HIT                    │
│                                 ▼               │                        │
│             ┌───────────────────────────────┐   │                        │
│             │       LangGraph Pipeline      │   │                        │
│             │  ① Classify (keyword→LLM)    │   │                        │
│             │  ② Rewrite  (HyDE expand)    │   │                        │
│             │  ③ Retrieve (ChromaDB MMR)   │   │                        │
│             │  ④ Rerank   (BM25 terms)     │   │                        │
│             │  ⑤ Generate (intent-routed)  │   │                        │
│             └──────────────┬────────────────┘   │                        │
│                            │ answer              │                        │
│                            ▼                     │                        │
│             ┌──────────────────────────────┐     │                        │
│             │   Log + Cache + Eval         │◀────┘                        │
│             │   latency · scores · sources │                              │
│             └──────────────┬───────────────┘                             │
│                            ▼                                              │
│             ┌──────────────────────────────┐                             │
│             │    Analytics Dashboard       │                             │
│             │  p95 · cost · hit@10 · SLO  │                             │
│             └──────────────────────────────┘                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 📊 Production Metrics (MacBook M2, llama3.1:8b)

| Metric | Value | SLO Target |
|---|---|---|
| **p50 latency** | ~1.8 s | < 2.0 s ✅ |
| **p95 latency** | ~4.2 s | < 5.0 s ✅ |
| **p99 latency** | ~7.1 s | < 10.0 s ✅ |
| **Cost / request** (gpt-4o-mini) | $0.00024 | < $0.01 ✅ |
| **Cache hit rate** (warm) | ~38% | > 20% ✅ |
| **Cache latency** | ~120 ms | — |
| **Latency reduction** | ~42% avg | — |
| **Faithfulness** (RAGAS) | 0.81 | > 0.70 ✅ |
| **Answer relevance** | 0.78 | > 0.70 ✅ |
| **hit@10 proxy** | 0.83 | > 0.70 ✅ |

